"{\"uid\": \"wired.com-story-paris-summer-olympics-2024-purple-track-athletics-mondo\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"THIS STORY ORIGINALLY appeared onWIRED en Espa\\u00f1oland has been translated from Spanish.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 86, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"THIS STORY ORIGINALLY\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 21}, {\"ngram\": \"onWIRED\", \"from\": 31, \"to\": 38}, {\"ngram\": \"Espa\\u00f1oland\", \"from\": 42, \"to\": 52}, {\"ngram\": \"Spanish\", \"from\": 78, \"to\": 85}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Traditionally, the athleticstrack in an Olympic stadium is red.\", \"from\": 88, \"to\": 151, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the athleticstrack\", \"from\": 103, \"to\": 121}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic stadium\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 143}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, at the 2024 Summer Olympics, it's purple, to match the event colors chosen by the Paris organizing committee.\", \"from\": 152, \"to\": 270, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 243, \"end\": 248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999780770852, \"rank\": 2.1922853307660356e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Summer Olympics\", \"from\": 164, \"to\": 188}, {\"ngram\": \"purple\", \"from\": 195, \"to\": 201}, {\"ngram\": \"the event colors\", \"from\": 212, \"to\": 228}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But there is another difference: It's made with recycled shells produced by the fishing industry, as part of the 2024 Olympics' commitment to sustainability.\", \"from\": 271, \"to\": 428, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another difference\", \"from\": 284, \"to\": 302}, {\"ngram\": \"recycled shells\", \"from\": 319, \"to\": 334}, {\"ngram\": \"the fishing industry\", \"from\": 347, \"to\": 367}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 372, \"to\": 376}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympics' commitment\", \"from\": 380, \"to\": 409}, {\"ngram\": \"sustainability\", \"from\": 413, \"to\": 427}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Resilient flooring, such as running-track flooring, is made using calcium carbonate, which is usually obtained through mining.\", \"from\": 430, \"to\": 556, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Resilient flooring\", \"from\": 430, \"to\": 448}, {\"ngram\": \"running-track flooring\", \"from\": 458, \"to\": 480}, {\"ngram\": \"calcium carbonate\", \"from\": 496, \"to\": 513}, {\"ngram\": \"mining\", \"from\": 549, \"to\": 555}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, the company that designed the track for the 2024 Summer Olympics, Mondo, teamed up with a fisher's cooperative to gather shells of bivalve mollusks from the Mediterranean Sea, such as mussels and clams, which are rich in the material.\", \"from\": 557, \"to\": 800, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 632, \"end\": 637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_Media\", \"score\": 0.7405554249299091, \"rank\": 0.3108828573954707, \"text\": \"Mondo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_Media\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_Media\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Instead, the company\", \"from\": 557, \"to\": 577}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 601}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Summer Olympics\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 630}, {\"ngram\": \"a fisher's cooperative\", \"from\": 654, \"to\": 676}, {\"ngram\": \"shells\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 693}, {\"ngram\": \"bivalve mollusks\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 713}, {\"ngram\": \"the Mediterranean Sea\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 740}, {\"ngram\": \"mussels\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 757}, {\"ngram\": \"clams\", \"from\": 762, \"to\": 767}, {\"ngram\": \"the material\", \"from\": 787, \"to\": 799}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The shells would have otherwise gone to waste.\", \"from\": 801, \"to\": 847, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The shells\", \"from\": 801, \"to\": 811}, {\"ngram\": \"waste\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 846}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The track is functionally the same as a traditional one, with the aim being to consolidate the creation of a new, resilient, sustainable sports flooring.\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 1002, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The track\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 858}, {\"ngram\": \"a traditional one\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 904}, {\"ngram\": \"the aim\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 918}, {\"ngram\": \"the creation\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 952}, {\"ngram\": \"a new, resilient, sustainable sports flooring\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 1001}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mondo teamed up withNieddittas, an Italian fishing cooperative specializing in mollusks, to get the materials it needed.\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1004, \"end\": 1009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_Media\", \"score\": 0.7405554249299091, \"rank\": 0.3108828573954707, \"text\": \"Mondo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_Media\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mondo_Media\"}, {\"begin\": 1039, \"end\": 1046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.8612176669698931, \"rank\": 0.1592917038892266, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"withNieddittas\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1034}, {\"ngram\": \"mollusks\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1091}, {\"ngram\": \"the materials\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1113}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Its fishers cleaned and dried waste shells from harvested mussels and clams, grounded them into a fine powder, and sent the material to the flooring manufacturer to make the track.\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1305, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Its fishers\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1136}, {\"ngram\": \"dried waste shell